{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/frontend/19-08-28/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"fullcalendar-띄우기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#fullcalendar-%EB%9D%84%EC%9A%B0%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"fullcalendar 띄우기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>FullCalendar 띄우기</h3>\n<p>일단 자세한 사용법을 익히기 전에 FullCalendar를 화면에 띄워보는것부터 시작합시다. <strong>Scrpit 태그를 통해 FullCalendar를 띄우는 방법</strong>을 설명하고 있으니, ES6 빌드 시스템으로 띄우고 싶으신 분은 <a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/docs/initialize-es6\">여기</a>를 참고하시길 바랍니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save @fullcalendar/core @fullcalendar/daygrid</code>로 fullcalendar를 다운로드합니다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>html 파일을 하나 만들고 <a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/docs/initialize-globals\">테스트 코드</a>를 붙여넣어 줍니다. 이 때 href 주소를 알맞게 설정해 주셔야 합니다.</p>\n<p>제 경우에는 html파일을 node_modules 폴더 밖에 생성했기 때문에href='./node_modules/@fullcalendar/core/main.css' 이런식으로 수정하였습니다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>생성한 html파일을 브라우저를 통해 열어보면 다음과 같이 캘린더가 출력됩니다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/21b4d/19-08-28-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.15789473684211%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/15813/19-08-28-1.webp 190w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/1cdb2/19-08-28-1.webp 380w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/9046c/19-08-28-1.webp 760w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/c89f9/19-08-28-1.webp 1140w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/af3f0/19-08-28-1.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/a2d4f/19-08-28-1.png 190w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/3f520/19-08-28-1.png 380w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/3c051/19-08-28-1.png 760w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/b5cea/19-08-28-1.png 1140w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/21b4d/19-08-28-1.png 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/3c051/19-08-28-1.png\"\n            alt=\"img\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"플러그인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"플러그인 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>플러그인</h3>\n<p>기본적인 세팅 말고 더 다양한 기능을 제공받고 싶다면, 플러그인을 설치한 뒤 <em>'plugins'</em> array 내 원하는 플러그인을 추가하시면 됩니다. <a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/docs/plugin-index\">이곳</a>에서 fullcalendar에서 제공하는 플러그인 목록을 확인하실 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save @fullcalendar/'플러그인 이름'</code>의 형태로 플러그인을 설치한 뒤 html 파일에 아래와 같은 소스코드를 추가합니다. (저는 일단 dateClick 기능을 위해서 interaction, dayGrid 플러그인을 추가하였습니다.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'./node_modules/@fullcalendar/core/main.js'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'./node_modules/@fullcalendar/daygrid/main.js'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'./node_modules/@fullcalendar/interaction/main.js'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> calendar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FullCalendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Calendar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>calendarEl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token string\">'dayGrid'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'interaction'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">dateClick</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Clicked on: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> info<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dateStr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이 결과로, 날짜 칸을 마우스로 클릭하면 alert창이 출력됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/21b4d/19-08-28-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.6842105263158%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/15813/19-08-28-2.webp 190w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/1cdb2/19-08-28-2.webp 380w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/9046c/19-08-28-2.webp 760w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/c89f9/19-08-28-2.webp 1140w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/af3f0/19-08-28-2.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/a2d4f/19-08-28-2.png 190w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/3f520/19-08-28-2.png 380w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/3c051/19-08-28-2.png 760w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/b5cea/19-08-28-2.png 1140w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/21b4d/19-08-28-2.png 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/3c051/19-08-28-2.png\"\n            alt=\"img\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"handler\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#handler\" aria-label=\"handler permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Handler</h3>\n<p>왜 alert창이 출력되었는지를 이해하기 위해서는 Handler를 알아야합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> calendar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FullCalendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Calendar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>calendarEl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'dayGrid'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'interaction'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token function-variable function\">dateClick</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Clicked on: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> info<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dateStr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>핸들러는 일종의 옵션이지만, 특별한 일이 발생할 때마다 호출되는 함수를 말합니다. 위의 코드에서 <code class=\"language-text\">dateClick: function(info){…}</code> 파트가 핸들러이기 때문에 dateClick 이벤트가 발생했을 때 그에 알맞은 함수가 실행된 것입니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">calendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'dateClick'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'clicked on '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> info<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dateStr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이와 같이 on, off 메소드를 활용하여 동적으로 핸들러를 추가하는 방법 또한 존재합니다. 핸들러 뿐만 아니라 FullCallendar 내 메소드로도 캘린더를 제어할 수 있으니 <a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/docs/Calendar-prev\">참고</a>하시기 바랍니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"event-옵션\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#event-%EC%98%B5%EC%85%98\" aria-label=\"event 옵션 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Event 옵션</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> calendar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FullCalendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Calendar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>calendarEl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'dayGrid'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'interaction'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token literal-property property\">events</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">id</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">title</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Test1'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">start</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'2019-08-22'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">end</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'2019-08-24'</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">id</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">title</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Test2'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">start</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'2019-08-21'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">end</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'2019-08-23'</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>events 라는 옵션을 추가하고, 객체 array 형태로 이벤트를 입력했습니다. 그리고 캘린더를 확인해봅시다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/21b4d/19-08-28-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.10526315789475%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/15813/19-08-28-3.webp 190w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/1cdb2/19-08-28-3.webp 380w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/9046c/19-08-28-3.webp 760w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/c89f9/19-08-28-3.webp 1140w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/af3f0/19-08-28-3.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/a2d4f/19-08-28-3.png 190w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/3f520/19-08-28-3.png 380w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/3c051/19-08-28-3.png 760w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/b5cea/19-08-28-3.png 1140w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/21b4d/19-08-28-3.png 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/3c051/19-08-28-3.png\"\n            alt=\"img\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이렇게 캘린더에서 잘 출력되는 것을 확인할 수 있습니다. events 객체에 어떤 key와 value를 적어야 하는지에 대한 설명은 이 <a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/docs/event-object\">링크</a>를 참고하시면 됩니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"geteventbyid-메소드\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#geteventbyid-%EB%A9%94%EC%86%8C%EB%93%9C\" aria-label=\"geteventbyid 메소드 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>getEventById 메소드</h3>\n<p>events에 대한 정보는 getEventById메소드를 통해 가져올 수 있습니다. 인자로 원하는 Id에 대한 정보를 넣어주시면 됩니다. 한번 위의 소스코드 상태에서 <code class=\"language-text\">console.log( calendar.getEventById(1))</code> 를 실행 해 보겠습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/21b4d/19-08-28-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.421052631578945%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/15813/19-08-28-4.webp 190w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/1cdb2/19-08-28-4.webp 380w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/9046c/19-08-28-4.webp 760w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/c89f9/19-08-28-4.webp 1140w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/af3f0/19-08-28-4.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/a2d4f/19-08-28-4.png 190w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/3f520/19-08-28-4.png 380w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/3c051/19-08-28-4.png 760w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/b5cea/19-08-28-4.png 1140w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/21b4d/19-08-28-4.png 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/3c051/19-08-28-4.png\"\n            alt=\"img\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이렇게 'id : 1' 값을 가진 events 데이터에 대한 정보가 출력된 것을 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"참고자료\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%90%EB%A3%8C\" aria-label=\"참고자료 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고자료</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/\">FullCalendar 공식 홈페이지</a><a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/#demos\">Demo 확인</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/#demos\">\n</a></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#fullcalendar-%EB%9D%84%EC%9A%B0%EA%B8%B0\">FullCalendar 띄우기</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8\">플러그인</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#handler\">Handler</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#event-%EC%98%B5%EC%85%98\">Event 옵션</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#geteventbyid-%EB%A9%94%EC%86%8C%EB%93%9C\">getEventById 메소드</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%90%EB%A3%8C\">참고자료</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"path":"/frontend/19-08-28/","title":"Script로 FullCalendar Events 띄우기","category":"FrontEnd","date":"2019-08-28"}}},"pageContext":{"postPath":"/frontend/19-